      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.GrafGen"
      },
      "sc:description": "To classify Helicobacter pylori genomes according to genetic distance from nine reference populations. The nine reference populations are hpgpAfrica, hpgpAfrica-distant, hpgpAfroamerica, hpgpEuroamerica, hpgpMediterranea, hpgpEurope, hpgpEurasia, hpgpAsia, and hpgpAklavik86-like. The vertex populations are Africa, Europe and Asia.",
